Package org.graffiti.plugins.ios.importers.graphml.parser

Class GraphMLEntityResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.graffiti.plugins.ios.importers.graphml.parser.GraphMLEntityResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.EntityResolver

    public class GraphMLEntityResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.xml.sax.EntityResolver
    Class GraphMLEntityResolver implements the EntityResolver interface to resolve external entities. In particular, the XML schemas of graphML referred to in the schema location of a graphML file shall be resolved using the locally cached version.
    Author:
    ruediger
